Package CS509.client.driver

Class Trip

java.lang.Object
CS509.client.driver.Trip
public class Trip extends Object
Trip is a representation of data pertinent to a flight reservation. The Trip object stores the ticket price, the length, and the arrival and departure dates. The trip is primarily composed though of a List of Flights (LoF) of class Flights.
